revision.text:
The '''1981 [[Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup|National Challenge Cup]]''' was the 68th edition of the USSF's annual open soccer championship. Teams from the [[North American Soccer League (1968–1984)|North American Soccer League]] declined to participate.  [[Maccabi Los Angeles|Maccabee A.C.]] defeated [[Brooklyn Dodgers S.C.|Brooklyn Dodgers]] in the final game. The score was 5-1.<ref>{{cite web|title=1981 US Open Cup|url=http://thecup.us/1981-us-open-cup-results/|publisher=TheCup.us|accessdate=5 June 2011}}</ref> 

