'''Hamhung Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Hamhung]], [[North Korea]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium holds 35,000 spectators and opened in 1981.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/asia/countries/north_korea.shtml |title=Stadiums in North Korea |date=2013-05-20 |work= |publisher=World Stadiums |accessdate=2013-05-20 |quote= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GkmApn1e |archivedate=2013-05-20 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>http://cafe.daum.net/stade/5BXH/66?docid=1DZEG5BXH6620110407124655</ref>
