The '''Côte d'Ivoire Davis Cup team''' represents [[Côte d'Ivoire]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Ivoirienne de Tennis]]. They have not competed since [[2012 Davis Cup|2012]].

Côte d'Ivoire have reached the promotion round of Group II on four occasions, but have never played in Group I.

==History==
Côte d'Ivoire competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1986 Davis Cup|1986]].

